Samuel  Belzberg's Experience
Title: President
               Company: Gibralt Capital Corporation
Job Details
               Gibralt Capital Corporation is a Vancouver, Canada based alternative asset manager. Gibralt focuses on investments that span the globe, but with a specific presence in North America. Gibralt's investments include private equity, real estate, public market securities, and credit-oriented funds. Gibralt's opportunistic strategy targets attractive absolute returns.These strategies may exhibit short term volatility, exposure to a less liquid set of investments and varying correlation to equity, credit and interest rate markets. They also may exhibit a higher degree of manager concentration relative to broadly diversified strategies in order to emphasize particularly attractive current market opportunities. Advantages for Partners with Gibralt Capital:Agile investment decision process;Execution experience - even in challenging markets - due to Gibralt's access to financing & syndication; andStrong relationships with corporations, governments, and high net worth investors, all to provide maximum return to business stakeholders. About Us | Team | Contact Us
Title: Founder
               Company: Balfour Holdings Inc
Job Details
               Balfour Holdings, Inc. is an independent consulting firm offering a full range of products and services to the gold mining and minerals industry. The company was formed from the working experiences of Douglas B. Silver in both large and small companies and has been expanded to address issues of critical concern to the minerals' industry. Balfour keeps abreast of important issues through its daily interaction with industry leaders, and by maintaining of an extensive corporate library and strong network. The collected information provides Balfour Holdings' clients with a competitive advantage because strategic problems can be scientifically analyzed and lead to better decision making. The company specializes in finding answers to difficult corporate issues through its international network of gold mining clients and contacts. It has successfully completed several hundred projects for junior and senior mining companies, merchant banks and private investors for a variety of commodities.
